{"tid":2012582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡狗屋情況","createTime":"2020-05-11T17:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T17:53:43.000Z","uid":19726,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"750cb99f375717e4468f50fed9a6bf8e8d002b65","tid":2012582,"uid":19726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:14:12.000Z","msg":"【昨晚被捕手足於<del>警署</del><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">狗屋</span></strong>內的情況】<br />\n<br />\n「你可以搵律師家人，但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋呢度冇電話喎</span></span>」<br />\n克警最初聲稱停車場的臨時拘留地方，沒有電話，致較前排手足未能聯絡家人及律師。<br />\n<br />\n「你搵律師都係乜都唔答㗎啦，早啲落咗口供早啲走」<br />\n克警向被捕人士表示若要律師陪同落口供，就必需<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">排到最後</span></span></strong>才處理，同時卻多番借詞推搪阻撓律師見被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚警方濫捕、不斷剝奪被捕人士權利，我們定必追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n#助理已報平安 #成晚冇瞓過晏晝仲要考試<br />\n#男女均於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">半開放地方搜身</span></strong><br />\n#整整12小時只坐在停車場乾等乾曬 <br />\n#0600落完口供 #1300先走得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 黃大仙區議員劉珈汶 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107497907250794/posts/244493423551241/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107497907250794%2Fposts%2F244493423551241%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=ae95b881\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107497907250794/posts/244493423551241/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"3264cb8f3128daecc3a5415c9378b0f5ce72f3bd","tid":2012582,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:17:01.000Z","msg":"你大聲D講如果係大陸一早比錢走得啦"},{"pid":"65ee078d909a28583d5db5dd098b7223adfc7052","tid":2012582,"uid":229834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3264cb8f3128daecc3a5415c9378b0f5ce72f3bd","tid":2012582,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:17:01.000Z","msg":"你大聲D講如果係大陸一早比錢走得啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"個個好似你咁拎住keyboard週街走咩